headline: Incyte price target raised to $70 from $68 at Wells Fargo
summary: Wells Fargo raised the firm’s price target on Incyte (INCY) to $70 from $68 and keeps an Equal Weight rating on the shares. The firm adjusted price targets in the Smid-cap biotechnology group as part of its 2025 outlook. Wells top sector picks target Ascendis Pharma (ASND), aTyr Pharma (ATYR), Rhythm Pharmaceuticals (RYTM), and Xencor (XNCR).
